headline: Take-Two Interactive: Too Expensive As Casual Gamers Have Infinite Options
summary: Take-Two Interactive stock is rated a "Sell" after a 35% rally and 50x FY27 EBITDA valuation. Here's what investors need to know about the gaming company.
